short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Switch between different search engines with a click

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With a single click, switch your search engine. supports using the IP LNQUIRE function and add custom searches.
One click will change the search engine in your address bar. allows for the addition of custom searches.
